#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:3
msgid "MPI Tools"
msgstr "MPI 工具"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:5
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "目錄"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:8
msgid "Core MPI Utilities"
msgstr "核心 MPI 工具"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_avg:1
msgid "Average a scalar or vector over MPI processes."
msgstr "在 MPI 程序間對純量或向量取平均值。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_fork:1
msgid "Re-launches the current script with workers linked by MPI."
msgstr "以 MPI 連結的 worker 重新啟動目前的腳本。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_fork:3
msgid "Also, terminates the original process that launched it."
msgstr "同時終止啟動它的原始程序。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_fork:5
msgid ""
"Taken almost without modification from the Baselines function of the "
"`same name`_."
msgstr ""
"幾乎未經修改地取自 Baselines 中 `same name`_ 的同名函式。"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "參數"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_fork:10
msgid "Number of process to split into."
msgstr "要分割成的程序數量。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_fork:12
msgid "Bind each MPI process to a core."
msgstr "將每個 MPI 程序綁定到一個 CPU 核心。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_statistics_scalar:1
msgid "Get mean/std and optional min/max of scalar x across MPI processes."
msgstr "取得純量 x 在所有 MPI 程序間的平均值／標準差，以及可選的最小值／最大值。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_statistics_scalar:3
msgid "An array containing samples of the scalar to produce statistics for."
msgstr "包含要計算統計量之純量樣本的陣列。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.mpi_statistics_scalar:5
msgid "If true, return min and max of x in addition to mean and std."
msgstr "如果為 true，除了平均值和標準差外，還回傳 x 的最小值和最大值。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.num_procs:1
msgid "Count active MPI processes."
msgstr "計算活躍的 MPI 程序數量。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_tools.proc_id:1
msgid "Get rank of calling process."
msgstr "取得呼叫程序的 rank。"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:15
msgid "MPI + PyTorch Utilities"
msgstr "MPI + PyTorch 工具"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:17
msgid ""
"``spinup.utils.mpi_pytorch`` contains a few tools to make it easy to do "
"data-parallel PyTorch optimization across MPI processes. The two main "
"ingredients are syncing parameters and averaging gradients before they "
"are used by the adaptive optimizer. Also there's a hacky fix for a "
"problem where the PyTorch instance in each separate process tries to get "
"too many threads, and they start to clobber each other."
msgstr ""
"``spinup.utils.mpi_pytorch`` 包含一些工具，使得跨 MPI 程序進行資料並行的 "
"PyTorch 最佳化變得容易。兩個主要組成部分是：在自適應最佳化器使用梯度之前，"
"同步參數和對梯度取平均值。此外還有一個針對以下問題的臨時修正：每個獨立程序中的 "
"PyTorch 實例嘗試取得過多的執行緒，導致它們開始互相干擾。"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:19
msgid "The pattern for using these tools looks something like this:"
msgstr "使用這些工具的模式大致如下："

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:21
msgid ""
"At the beginning of the training script, call "
"``setup_pytorch_for_mpi()``. (Avoids clobbering problem.)"
msgstr ""
"在訓練腳本的開頭，呼叫 ``setup_pytorch_for_mpi()``。（避免互相干擾的問題。）"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:23
msgid "After you've constructed a PyTorch module, call ``sync_params(module)``."
msgstr "在建構好 PyTorch module 後，呼叫 ``sync_params(module)``。"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:25
msgid ""
"Then, during gradient descent, call ``mpi_avg_grads`` after the backward "
"pass, like so:"
msgstr ""
"然後，在梯度下降過程中，在反向傳播（backward pass）之後呼叫 ``mpi_avg_grads``，"
"如下所示："

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_pytorch.mpi_avg_grads:1
msgid "Average contents of gradient buffers across MPI processes."
msgstr "在 MPI 程序間對梯度緩衝區的內容取平均值。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_pytorch.setup_pytorch_for_mpi:1
msgid ""
"Avoid slowdowns caused by each separate process's PyTorch using more than"
" its fair share of CPU resources."
msgstr ""
"避免因每個獨立程序的 PyTorch 使用超過其合理份額的 CPU 資源而導致的效能下降。"

#: of spinup.utils.mpi_pytorch.sync_params:1
msgid "Sync all parameters of module across all MPI processes."
msgstr "在所有 MPI 程序間同步 module 的所有參數。"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:40
msgid "MPI + Tensorflow Utilities"
msgstr "MPI + Tensorflow 工具"

#: ../../utils/mpi.rst:42
msgid ""
"The ``spinup.utils.mpi_tf`` contains a a few tools to make it easy to use"
" the AdamOptimizer across many MPI processes. This is a bit hacky---if "
"you're looking for something more sophisticated and general-purpose, "
"consider `horovod`_."
msgstr ""
"``spinup.utils.mpi_tf`` 包含一些工具，使得跨多個 MPI 程序使用 AdamOptimizer "
"變得容易。這種做法有點不正規——如果你需要更精緻且通用的方案，請考慮使用 "
"`horovod`_。"
